::DeathScythe::

DeathScythe rounds a corner. He was still in the Cybertronian Fire. So far, 
his cloaking device had prevented the interior defences from detecting him, 
but he was getting agitated. He had no idea where he was, for all he knew he 
could be aproaching a dangerous portion of the ship.

DeathScythe keeps walking, cursing under his breath.
